HotelRoom

public HotelRoom(java.lang.String... strings)
Constructor for the HotelRoom pojo. Because the output of the Data.readRecord(String) method looks like 
0. |Palace                                                          |
1. |Smallville                                                      |
2. |2   |
3. |Y|
4. |$150.00 |
5. |2005/07/27|
6. |        |
for an unbooked room, it must be heavily parsed.

Parameters:
strings - An array of strings ordered to follow the output of he Data.readRecord(String) method.
